traits.locale_text:
This ability can only target allies who have enemies adjacent to them.{br}
Until the start of the Leader's next turn, all melee attacks made by the target deal additional damage equal to <u>(Leader's FEL bonus/2)</u> multiplied by the number of enemies adjacent to the target when this ability is used.{br}
If the target is under the effect of <b>Voice of Command</b>, it immediately makes an attack of opportunity against the adjacent enemy with the lowest remaining wounds.
